rComments: Professor Viola has been a true gem, she is very caring and kindhearted. She knows her material extremely well and makes the best jokes (history related). She answers every question and she tries to interact with her students. She is very helpful with the material (it was pre tough).
Best professor ever. I took this class in 1992 and I still think fondly of the class, thanks to her.

She is extremely hard working and punctual. You hand stuff in, its graded next week. She is so organized, passionate and treats students like adults. Grades tough but fair. Only prof at U of T who would see me anytime and give some direction in life. To her you aren't a number and she really tries to help with any problem. She is just a good person
Best prof EVER. SO helpful and really cares about students. I you like Russia or 20th C History, this is THE class to take.
